label_mapping.label: auto_starting_position
label_mapping.description: Robot starting location (by driver station or field zone)

label_mapping.label: Auto Total Points
label_mapping.description: Total number of points scored by the robot during the autonomous period.
label_mapping.usage_context: Recorded after the autonomous period ends, based on the robot's scoring actions as shown on the field display or by manual tally.

label_mapping.label: Teleop CORAL Scored in Branch (L2-L4)
label_mapping.description: Number of CORAL scored in the Branch (levels 2-4) during the teleoperated period.
label_mapping.usage_context: Tracked live during the teleop period as robots score CORAL in Branch goals at levels 2 through 4.

label_mapping.label: teleop_coral_L1_scored
label_mapping.description: Number of CORAL scored in the REEF trough (L1) during teleop

label_mapping.label: teleop_algae_scored_barge_processor
label_mapping.description: Number of ALGAE scored in the Barge and Processor goals during teleoperated period.
label_mapping.usage_context: Tracked live during the teleop phase as each ALGAE piece is scored in either the Barge or Processor goals.

label_mapping.label: tele_algae_bleed
label_mapping.description: Number of ALGAE game pieces unintentionally sent to the opposing side during teleop.
label_mapping.usage_context: Track each time a team accidentally causes an ALGAE piece to cross into the opposing field during the teleoperated period.

label_mapping.label: scout_comments
label_mapping.description: Free-form notes for recording observations or strategic insights about a team's performance during a match.
label_mapping.usage_context: Entered by scouts during or immediately after a match to capture details not covered by other metrics, such as unique strategies, robot issues, or alliance interactions.

label_mapping.label: endgame_total_points
label_mapping.description: Total points earned by the team during the endgame period of the match.
label_mapping.usage_context: Recorded at the end of the match by summing all points scored by the team during the endgame phase.
